# Hangout Planner

## Description
This project is an application that's built with React, Node.js and MongoDB. This application helps users who can't plan a new hangout by offering users an way to easily find new locations to add to an plan. It allow's the users to edit the their plan and dwell into further details about the locations.

## Features
Users can create an account to save their plans
Can interact with the map to find new locations depending on what type of place
Can save the location into a plan
Allow users to edit their plans by changing the name of the plan or deleting it.

## Installation

1. Clone the repository

```powershell
https://github.com/Lindanny9721/Capstone.git
cd capstone
```
2. Install dependencies for frontend and backend

```powershell
cd frontend
npm install
cd backend
npm install
```

3. Set up environment variables
For backend
```powershell
GOOGLE_MAPS_API_KEY = GOOGLE-APY-KEY
MONGO_URI= MONGODB_URI
JWT_SECRET = JWT_TOKEN
```
For frontend
```powershell
GOOGLE_MAPS_API_KEY = GOOGLE-APY-KEY
```
4. Start the servers

In the backend
```powershell
npm run start
```
In the frontend
```powershell
npm run dev
```

4. Technologies
React
Node.js Express.js
MongoDB Mongoose

